end
data.description: Optional end value of the time range. Format yyyy-mm-dd. Defaults to yesterday.

data.name: grouping
data.description: One of 'hour', 'day', 'week', 'month'. Specifies the granularity of the results. For example, in a day grouping one value is returned for each day of the time range. In a hour grouping one value is returned for every hour.

data.name: start
data.description: Optional start value of the time range. Format yyyy-mm-dd, for example 2013-01-01. Default value is dependent on the specified grouping.

data.name: type
data.description: Either 'views' or 'bytes'. Specifies if the results should be view counts or bytes. Defaults to 'views'.
